~~~~~~~~~
REQUIRES
~~~~~~~~~

Python2.7+
This is necessary for libraries.


~~~~~~~~~
LogFormat
~~~~~~~~~
Every Nginx virtual host you want to monitor needs to use combined2 defined in this way:

    log_format combined2 '$remote_addr - $remote_user [$time_local]  '
                    '"$request" $status $body_bytes_sent '
                    '"$http_referer" "$http_user_agent" [[$request_time]]';

